cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper involves machine learning techniques for robots to learn new skills from a single demonstration. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with learning from visual inputs. Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it deals with robots learning new skills. Finally, the paper involves systems and control (cs.SY) as it deals with robots acquiring new skills in complex unstructured environments.
